high_descs: Walk forward, then hang a left and walk over to the stove.
Pick up the pan on the back left burner of the stove.
Turn left and walk over to the fridge.
Put the pan in the fridge for a couple seconds to get cold, then take it out.
Turn right and walk to the section of counter to the left of the oven.
Put the chilled pan on the back of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left, move to the stove on the left.
Pick up the left pan on the stove.
Bring the pan to the fridge on the left of the stove.
Chill the pan in the fridge.
Bring the chilled pan to the counter to the right, between the fridge and stove.
Put the chilled pan on the back of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on the counter.

high_descs: Pick up the top left pot.
Carry the pot to the fridge.
Open fridge, place pot in fridge, close fridge, open fridge, take pot out.
Go to cabinet by the stove.
Place pot behind the big pot.
